<p>Texas&nbsp;does not&nbsp;offer online voter registration.&nbsp;For information on how to register to vote or update your registration, visit the state's voter registration information webpage: <a href="http://www.votetexas.gov/register-to-vote/index.html" target="_blank">http://www.votetexas.gov/register-to-vote/index.html​</a>.</p>

